          "locale_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«Si sobrevivimos, ¿qué hará después?».",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-04T14:13:35.8667114Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-04T14:13:35.8667115Z",
      "original_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-04T14:13:35.8667121Z",
          "locale_text": "«Si sobrevivimos, ¿qué hará después?»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「もし生き延びたら、君はその後どうするつもりだ？」",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-05T10:19:09.4864146Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-05T14:14:42.4575264Z",
      "original_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "AIGenerated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-05T14:14:42.4575269Z",
          "locale_text": "「もし生き延びたら、君はその後どうするつもりだ？」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“如果我们能活下来，之后你打算做什么？”",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-05T11:19:17.4606731Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-05T11:19:17.4606737Z",
      "original_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-05T11:19:17.4606750Z",
          "locale_text": "“如果我们能活下来，之后你打算做什么？”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Was habt Ihr vor, falls wir überleben?\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-10T14:19:52.4781700Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-10T14:19:52.4781701Z",
      "original_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-10T14:19:52.4781710Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Was habt Ihr vor, falls wir überleben?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Qu'avez-vous prévu de faire si nous survivons ? »",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-07T13:58:24.5879952Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-07T13:58:24.5879954Z",
      "original_text": "\"If we survive, what will you do after?\"",
